headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Keysight Technologies (KEYS) After Its Recent 26.6% Share Price Rise?
summary: If you are wondering whether Keysight Technologies is still good value at around US$223 per share, you are not alone. This article is built to help you frame that question clearly. Over the last year the stock has returned 26.6%, with 4.2% over the past 7 days and 8.1% over the last month and year to date, which may have shifted how some investors see its potential and risk. headline: Keysight (KEYS): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: What a time it’s been for Keysight. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has increased by a massive 40.4%, setting a new 52-week high of $227.13 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
